e.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Courtney-Thurston-Marianne-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courtney-love">Courtney Love</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thurston-moore">Thurston Moore</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/my-bloody-valentine">《My Bloody Valentine</a> 》的 Deb Googe 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/portishead">Portishead</a>的 Adrian Utley 一直在伦敦 Konk Studios 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey 的</a>合作者 Rob Ellis 合作开展一个项目。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="286" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-hole-solo-music-liverpool-interview-2819456"><b>Courtney Love：“我感觉自己是摇滚史上最幸运的混蛋”</b></a></li></ul><p>根据 Googe 周二（9 月 10 日）分享的 Instagram 帖子，他们似乎正在制作 Marianne Faithfull 封面项目。</p><p>在帖子中，古奇写道，“我在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kinks">奇想乐队</a>的工作室里度过了一天，翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marianne-faithfull">玛丽安·费斯福尔的</a>歌曲”，并附上了工作室的一系列照片。</p><p>制片人本·克里斯托弗斯 (Ben Christophers)<a href="https://ww