) 出席 2024 年 MTV 视频音乐奖颁奖典礼。 （迈克·科波拉 / Getty Images for MTV 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Victoria-De-Angelis-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Måneskin">Måneskin</a>的<a href="/artists/Victoria-De-Angelis">维多利亚·德·安吉利斯 (Victoria De Angelis)</a>接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了她与<a href="/artists/Anitta">安妮塔 (Anitta)</a>合作的新个人事业以及这支意大利摇滚乐队的未来。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/maneskin-cover-interview-2022-supermodel-3233987">封面上的 Måneskin：“没有人能让摇滚乐继续存在——它是不可能被杀死的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队的贝斯手 De Angelis 凭借歌曲“Zitti E Buoni”首次成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/eurovision-2021-james-newman-italy-2946370">2021 年欧洲歌唱大赛的获胜者</a>，最近宣布了她的新独奏项目，该项目将她标志性的摇滚声音换成 DJ 套牌等更多舞蹈俱乐部准备就绪。</p><p>上周（9月3日），她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskins-victoria-de-angelis-launches-solo-career-with-techno-banger-get-up-bitch-shake-ya-ass-with-anitta-3790132">发行了首张单曲“GET UP BITCH！” (Shake Ya Ass)&#39;</a> – 一首充满活力的舞曲，融合了活泼的 techno 和 baile funk，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/meet-anitta-brazilian-pop-megastar-music-world-underestimates-powerful-women-like-2349938">巴西巨星</a>演唱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="维多利亚，安妮塔 - 起来吧！摇你的屁股（与安妮塔）（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-RYC77nQKAE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>谈到这次合作，De Angelis 告诉我们：“我刚刚向她发送了我制作的演示，我当时想，‘我有这首歌，我认为让你参与其中会很恶心’，之后她就把这首歌发给了我。一周。</p><p> “我在飞机上用我买的小 Wi-Fi 下载了它，我当时就想，‘啊’，在飞机上摇晃我的屁股。我爱安妮塔，她太棒了，所以这是一次完美的合作。”</p><p>这位音乐家还讨论了声音方向的明显变化，抛弃了 Måneskin 的硬摇滚，透露了她对“百乐放克和巴西拉丁俱乐部音乐”的热爱，并通过“GET UP BITCH!”分享了这一点。 （Shake Ya Ass）”是“我喜欢的所有声音与硬科技的完美结合。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_042J7S-BL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 